title: Gucci Soho Medium Shoulder Bag
description: Gucci Soho medium shoulder bag in metallic khaki calfskin leather. Featuring metal-toned hardware, embossed interlocking GG logo, and detachable leather tassel at front. The hook closure opens to a cream textile interior with a zipper and patch pockets. Approximate dimensions: 37cm(Base-L) x 26cm(H) x 14cm(D), double chain shoulder strap drop 18.5cm. Accompanied by a Gucci dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned).
